## ğŸš— 4. Dijkstraâ€™s Algorithm (Shortest Path)

**Concept:**
Given a weighted graph and a **source vertex**, find the **shortest distance** from that source to **all other vertices**.

**Approach:**
Greedy choice â€” har step par **minimum distance vertex** choose karo aur uske neighbours update karo (relaxation).

**Use kab karte hain:**
Jab question me bola ho â€”

> â€œFind shortest pathâ€, â€œminimum distanceâ€, â€œleast cost routeâ€, â€œnetwork routingâ€, â€œmap navigationâ€
> â†’ **Use Dijkstraâ€™s Algorithm.**

**Important:**

* Works only for **non-negative weights**.
* If negative edges present â†’ **use Bellman-Ford algorithm**.

